name: Capsule Points
description:
:::Capsule Points:::
You can get points from Cash/Mito Capsule boxes.
With 100 points, you can get a ST Vehicle Ticket.

name: ST Vehicle Ticke
description:
:::ST Vehicle Ticket:::
Right click to get the new ST model with 100 probability.

name: Master Key
description:
Master Key that can be used to open the Locked Box.
By right-clicking, a key will be used to unlock
a Locked Box.

name: Locked Box
description:
Tightly Locked Box.
You can purchase the Master key from the shop while the event is being held. The content may vary depending on the key you use.

name: Openable Box
description:
The box that becam openable by using a key.
By right clicking, you can get an item such as Mittron Enhancer Deluxe, Transition Liquid, some MITO or etc.
If lucky, you can also get Broken.

Be aware that the box will become useless if now used in time.

name: Useless Box
description:
A box that was not used in time and became unusable.
Let's throw away this box since it's useless.
